OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs after seven-month wait for home
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FElaine Willcox paid a visit to
OL,8,FStephen's home to see how the cramped
OL,9,Fconditions are affecting his family.
OL,11,FA father who has to carry his disabled
OL,12,Fson up flights of stairs multiple
OL,13,Ftimes a day says it is impossible to
OL,14,Fgive "his children a better life"
OL,15,Funtil they find a suitable home.
OL,17,FStephen Murray currently lives with
OL,18,Fhis four sons in his one bedroom flat
OL,19,Fin Widnes, Chehsire, where they are
OL,20,Fall forced to sleep in the same room.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
