OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs after seven-month wait for home
OL,6,FThe lack of space makes it impossible
OL,7,Ffor Stephen's seven-year-old son
OL,8,FHarry, who has cerebral palsy, to use
OL,9,Fhis wheelchair or mobility aids to
OL,10,Fmove around the house - which could
OL,11,Fhave a lifelong impact on his mobility.
OL,13,FIn their bedroom, Stephen explains: In
OL,14,F(one) bed is Kade and Kaylum, and the
OL,15,Fone that's folded up is where my 18-
OL,16,Fyear-old sleeps. But my mum passed
OL,17,Faway on Mother's Day so he's sleeping
OL,18,Fat my dad's at the moment.
