OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F398A1747315525
OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs after seven-month wait for home
OL,6,F"And then on that bed there is where
OL,7,Fme and Harry sleep. There's five of us
OL,8,Fin one room."
OL,10,FDespite Stephen searching every night
OL,11,Fon his Housing Association's property
OL,12,Fpool, he is yet to find anywhere with
OL,13,Fenough room.
OL,15,FHe said: "I don't feel like I'm
OL,16,Fgetting any support. I had to take my
OL,17,Fchildren away from the situation they
OL,18,Fwere in to give them a better life,
OL,19,Fbut I feel like they've gone backwards.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
