OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs after seven-month wait for home
OL,6,FHis older brother Kade said: "I love
OL,7,F(Harry). I love him with all my heart,
OL,8,Fand I want him to be happy but right
OL,9,Fnow he can't be happy because he can't
OL,10,Fget what he needs."
OL,12,FHis other brother Kaylum added: "What
OL,13,Fif my dad falls? What would happen
OL,14,Fthen with Harry? All we need is a
OL,15,Fhouse with enough bedrooms for us."
OL,17,FTheir father Stephen has been
OL,18,Fsearching for a suitable home for
OL,19,Fseven months, and despite successfully
OL,20,Fbidding on three properties all of the
OL,21,Foffers were eventually withdrawn.
