OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs after seven-month wait for home
OL,6,FBut Stephen's local MP Derek Twigg
OL,7,Fsays he is "very unhappy" with Halton
OL,8,FHousing's response, claiming there is
OL,9,Fno "adequate explanation given" about
OL,10,Fthe withdrawals of previous offers.
OL,12,FHe said: "Halton Housing advised that
OL,13,Fthere was no date available for when
OL,14,Fthis family will be adequately housed
OL,15,Fand no adequate explanation given
OL,16,Fabout why the previous house offer was
OL,17,Fwithdrawn.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
